title: Nabakari Bitch To Incubus
alternative_title: 名ばかりビッチと陰キャバス
status: 名ばかりビッチと陰キャバス
description:
Description :
        Yumeshi, an introverted incubus, is unexpectedly ordered by his succubus mother to "lose his virginity." In a state of confusion, he decides to approach a girl in his class who has a reputation for being a troublemaker. However, he soon discovers that this girl has a surprisingly troubled and innocent past of her own...!?
